cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.DB, cs.SE 

This paper focuses on trust mechanisms for data sharing in smart cities, which involves aspects of cybersecurity (cs.CR), data management (cs.DB), and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of semantic technology and reasoning also suggests a potential fit for the sub-categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
